---
title: Chicken Curry with Ballymaloe Relish with broccolini and rice
description: Korma paste and North Indian spices join forces in this creamy chicken curry to create a warming weeknight meal. Finish with a dollop of Ballymaloe relish on top for a fruity addition to your dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R01_W34_IE_IECC26898-2_Main_PHOTO_edit_6_high-30670d2c.jpg
